burlap.behavior.functionapproximation

Class FunctionGradient.SparseGradient

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.behavior.functionapproximation.FunctionGradient.SparseGradient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FunctionGradient
    Enclosing interface:
    FunctionGradient

    public static class FunctionGradient.SparseGradient
extends Object
implements FunctionGradient
    A sparse FunctionGradient that only explicitly stores the partial derivative for parameters with non-zero partial derivatives. The partial derivative for parameters not explicitly stored will have a value of zero returned.
